dataIdInfo.idAbs:
This feature class contains NAVTEQ street features for the 21 counties in the CMAP Modeling Area. This file was extracted from a larger "Midwest" NAVTEQ file which we received through a data-sharing agreement with IDOT. It was modified from the original delivery in the following ways: 1) Data extracted for these counties (plus a five-mile buffer): ILLINOIS: Cook, DuPage, Kane, Kendall, Lake, McHenry,Will, Boone, DeKalb, Winnebago, Lee, Ogle, Grundy, LaSalle, Kankakee. INDIANA: Lake, Porter, LaPorte. WISCONSIN: Kenosha, Racine, Walworth 2) Data were projected from the native WGS Lat/Lon coordinate system to the Illinois State Plane East (NAD83) coordinate system.
